text: Facelina vicina is a species of sea slug, an aeolid nudibranch, a marine gastropod mollusc in the family Facelinidae.MolluscaBase (2018). Facelina vicina (Bergh, 1882). Accessed on 2018-02-17. ==Distribution== This species was described from Trieste, Adriatic Sea. ==References== Category:Facelinidae Category:Gastropods described in 1882
title: Facelina vicina
